videos.headline: Eastern Michigan ties game with one-handed touchdown catch
videos.description: Eastern Michigan's Gunnar Oakes makes a one-handed catch in the end zone for a 16-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Eastern Michigan takes first lead with 4-yard TD
videos.description: Mike Glass III runs the ball into the end zone for a 4-yard Eastern Michigan touchdown, giving  the Eagles their first lead of the game.

videos.headline: Bellamy finds the gap for 15-yard TD
videos.description: LeVante Bellamy fights off the defenders for a 15-yard Western Michigan touchdown run.
